works.description:
This blog was created by one of our
chapters, Prevent Child Abuse Wyoming, that had rights to the name. That
chapter closed Dec 31, 2000 and thus the rights of the stay with the parent
organization, Prevent Child Abuse America. It appears that the former
chapter did not take the blog down. Can you take the blog down as they no
longer exist?
Thank you.
Sincerely,

Barbara Shaffer
